title: Goodbye Mr. Mackenzie - 1989 - Fish Heads And Tails
description:
10 track album by a group Goodbye Mr. Mackenzie, which is known as act where Shirley Manson from Garbage started as backing vocalist.

All tracks are 128 kbps and in wma format.

If you have other albums of Goodbye Mr. Mackenzie, please share.

Another very-cool-and-hard-to-find band from 80s AOR/mainstream rock, which is in my wish list, is DARLING CRUEL. Looking for their album "Passion Crimes" (1989).
